T02D3767:127a-4: thugs rje chen po rnam par skyob la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3767:127a-6: rin chen rang bzhin ngos mnyam la //
T02D3767:127b-0: dri zhim pa yi byug @127b pas byug / mu tig me tog nor bu dgod //
T02D3767:127b-2: me tog dmar pos bon can //
T02D3767:127b-3: bzhag la de steng thub pa bzhugs //
T02D3767:127b-4: gdugs dkar gyis ni steng nas dbub //
T02D3767:127b-5: sgrub po padma'i phreng ba yi //
T02D3767:127b-6: nga rgyal 'dzin pas rdo rje'i lag / gnyis gshibs gyen du bskyod pa'i rgyas //
T02D3767:127b-7: sa gsum gtso bo spar bar bya //
T02D3767:127b-8: rab tu dbyibs legs kha dog mdzes //
T02D3767:127b-9: dri bsung ro mchog reg bzang ba'i //
T02D3767:127b-10: me tog spungs pas go rims bzhin //
T02D3767:127b-11: gling sogs bkod pa ji bzhin brtag / aom a'a:badzra tsa tu ra dhv'i pa h'um //
T02D3767:127b-12: aom a'a:badzra pa y'ashta dv'i pa h'um /
T02D3767:127b-14: aom a'a: badzr'a shta mangga la h'um /
T02D3767:127b-15: aom a'a: badzra siddhi bim sha ti h'um /
T02D3767:127b-16: aom a'a: badzra s'urya tsandra h'um /
T02D3767:127b-17: rnam dag gzhing du phun tshogs gling dang rin chen dang //
T02D3767:127b-18: bkra shis grub pa rim gsum phreng ba legs bkod la //
T02D3767:127b-19: gsal byed sgron ma 'bar ba gnyis kyis brgyan gyur pa //
T02D3767:127b-20: sngags 'chang rdo rje rol pa'i gar gyi bstabs pas dbul //
T02D3767:127b-21: de nas lus can thams cad la //
T02D3767:127b-22: 'jig rten mgon po nyer mkho'i gzugs //
T02D3767:127b-23: dpag med rnam par 'phrul pa yis //
T02D3767:127b-24: zhing rnams kun du don yod spyod //
T02D3767:127b-25: ji srid snying po byang chub bar //
T02D3767:127b-26: de dag nam yang 'dren pa'i mthus //
T02D3767:127b-27: ngan 'gro'i sgra yang mi grag cing //
T02D3767:127b-28: rtag tu dga' skyid 'tsho bar byed //
T02D3767:127b-29: gal te blo gsal spobs spyod na //
T02D3767:127b-30: sku gsungs la sogs gang bshad pa //
T02D3767:127b-31: cho ga de dag 'das pa yang //
T02D3767:127b-32: gdon mi za bar bya ba nyid //
T02D3767:127b-33: gang tshe bsdu bar 'dod pa na //
T02D3767:127b-34: se gol brdabs pas spar byas la /
T02D3767:127b-35: bzod par gsol dang smon lam gdab //
T02D3767:127b-36: dran pa'i rgyu yis gzugs gdab bya //
T02D3767:127b-37: mandal gyi cho ga kha che'i pan chen gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
